reviews.review_text: Pure Audio Bliss Thank you H/S,Thank you Charlie Miller.Jerry sounds amazing on this.Listen loud & #dontletgo

- Already heard part of this on the download series issue, and the only problem I have with it is that, as with many early 80s renditions of Eyes, they play it too fast...by too fast I mean faster than they're actually capable of playing while staying on the beat. Other than that the show is spectacular, but I hate it when they ruin Eyes like that. I don't care how fast you can play; I care that it sounds good when you play it.
